	<a class="sidebar-button__text" href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/news/"><img class="sidebar-button__icon" src="https://www.whitehouse.gov/wp-content/themes/whitehouse/assets/img/menu-large.svg" alt="menu" />All News</a>
